<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Offer Letter</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-SnH5WK+bZxgPHs44uWIX+LLJAJ9/2PkPKZ5QiAj6Ta86w+fsb2TkcmfRyVX3pBnMFcV7oQPJkl9QevSCWr3W6A==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    position: relative;
}

.header {
    width: 100%;
    height: 120px;
    background-color: #003366;
    position: relative;
}

.header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 90%;
    right: 70px;
    background: black;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    bottom: -187px;
}

.blue-strip {
    position: absolute;
    top: 29px;
    right: 154px;
    width: 128px;
    height: 100%;
    rotate: 315deg;
    background-color: #003366;
    transform: skewX(4deg);
    transform-origin: top right;
    z-index: 2;
}

.darker-blue-strip {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-bottom: 256px solid transparent;
    border-right: 273px solid #004e99;
    z-index: 2;
}

.darker-blue-strip::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -15px;
    width: 15px;
    height: 100%;
    box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 0px 54px 55px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px -12px 30px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 4px 6px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.17) 0px 12px 13px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.09) 0px -3px 5px;
}

.yellow-triangle {
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    right: 100px;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-left: 100px solid #ffcc00;
    border-bottom: 100px solid transparent;
    z-index: 3;
}

.logo {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

.logo img {
    height: 150px;
    margin-left: 15px;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
}

.content {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.ref-no {
    margin-left: 110px;
}

.date-ref {
    margin-top: 60px;
    margin-left: 590px;
}

.recipient-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin-left: 110px;
}

.info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
}

.degree-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
}
.degree-info h2{
    font-size: 18px;
}
.letter-content {
    margin-top: 30px;
    width: 70%;
    margin-left: 205px;
}

.offer-letter-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.letter-content h2 {
    margin-top: 25px;
}

.internship-details {
    padding: 14px 0px 19px 41px;
}

.signature {
    margin-top: 60px;
    display: flex;
}

.signatory {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.signatory p {
    font-weight: 600;
}

.powered-by {
    text-align: center;
    color: #004e99;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    margin-top: 60px;
    font-weight: 600;
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #003366;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
}

.footer .footer-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.footer .footer-info p {
    margin: 5px 0;
}

.footer .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 10px;
    left: 80px;
    position: relative;
}

.footer .contact-info p {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
}

.footer .contact-detail {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 400px;
}

.footer .footer-design {
    position: relative;
    background-color: #003366;
}

.footer .footer-design .blue-strip {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 29px;
    left: 51px;
    top: -247px;
    height: 120px;
    rotate: 45deg;
    background-color: #003366;
    transform-origin: bottom left;
    transform: skewX(338deg) skewX(10deg);
    z-index: 2;
}

.footer .footer-design .darker-blue-strip {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    top: -236px;
    border-bottom: 256px solid #004e99;
    border-right: 273px solid transparent;
    z-index: 2;
}

.footer .footer-design .yellow-triangle {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    top: -45px;
    transform: rotate(270deg);
    border-left: 65px solid rgb(255, 204, 0);
    border-bottom: 65px solid transparent;
    z-index: 3;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header">
            <div class="blue-strip"></div>
            <div class="darker-blue-strip"></div>
            <div class="yellow-triangle"></div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="Images/logo.png" alt="Techskill Solutions Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <div>
                <h2 class="ref-no">Ref. No.: <%= @user.reference_number %></h2>
                <h2 class="date-ref">Date: <%= Date.today %></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="recipient-info">
                <h2>To,</h2>
                <h2 class="info" style="display: flex;">Name: <p><%= @user.student_name %></p></h2>
                <div class="degree-info"><h2><%= @user.course %></h2><h2>in</h2><h2><%= @user.branch %></h2></div>
                <h2 class="info">Semester: <p><%= @user.semester %></p></h2>
                <h2 class="info">Enrollment No.: <p><%= @user.enrollment_number %></p></h2>
                <h2 class="info">College Name: <p><%= @user.college_name %></p></h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="offer-letter-title">Offer Letter</h3>
        <div class="letter-content">
            <h2>Dear <%= @user.student_name %>,</h2>
            <p>We are delighted to extend an internship offer for the position of Software
                Development Intern at Techskill Solutions effective from  <%= @user.internship_start_date %>.
                You have to complete your daily task within a time limit. After
                successful completion of an internship, a certificate will be issued.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <h4>Internship Details</h4>
                <div class="internship-details">
                    <li>Start Date: <%= @user.internship_start_date %></li>
                    <li>End Date: <%= @user.internship_end_date %></li>
                </div>
            </ul>
            <p>We are excited about the prospect of working with you and believe this
                internship will offer valuable learning opportunities.
            </p>
            <p>
                Warm regards,
            </p>
            <div class="signature">
                <div class="signatory">
                    <p>Authorized Signatory</p>
                    <p>Techskill Solutions</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="powered-by">Powered by SoftCoding Solutions</p>
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-info">
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <div class="contact-detail">
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i>www.techskillsolutions.in</p>
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>+91 8511245350</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>contact@techskillsolutions.com</p>
                    <p><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>204, CopperLeaf, Nr. Bhuyangdev Cross Road, Nr. Parshwanath Jainmandir BRTS, Sola Road, Ahmedabad-380061</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-design">
            <div class="blue-strip"></div>
            <div class="darker-blue-strip"></div>
            <div class="yellow-triangle"></div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
